creator: Different Technologies
descriptionHtml:
We make rentals better for tenants. If you’re a tenant who lives in a property managed by different, you’ll need our app. But you won’t just need it, you’ll want it. We want to make your life easier as a tenant because good tenants make for happy owners.

We’ve designed and built the app so that you have the best possible day-to-day tenant experience. Our app makes it easy to:
- Pay your rent on time every month automatically
- Submit maintenance requests
- Sign and access your important tenancy documents
- Get in touch with us quickly and easily

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Welcome to the brand new tenant app! Our tenant app underwent some renovation and is getting cleaner, faster, and smarter. It’s the post-lockdown glow-up you were hoping for!

✦ Everything that needs your attention at an eye’s glance
✦ Pay your rent exactly the way you want
✦ Always know what’s going on with your maintenance requests

Please note that this is a beta version of the app which is still undergoing final testing before its official release.

title: Different for tenants

creator: Different Technologies
descriptionHtml:
We’re here to make your rental feel like home. From getting maintenance issues sorted to keeping you in the loop, we’ve got your back.

KEY FEATURES:
* Pay your rent with ease: Simply upload your preferred payment method and off you go. All payments can easily be made through your app.
* Quickly log maintenance issues: Follow our intuitive prompts, fill out a short description and upload photos and videos to get repairs sorted sooner.
* Check the status of logged issues: Never wonder where your repairs are up to with our handy status tracker, available 24/7 within your app.
* Access your documents on the go: All the important docs for your tenancy are stored in your app for easy access.
descriptionShort: We make your rental feel like home

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: - Minor bug fixes and performance improvements
